text: The Bank of Guangzhou Tower is a fifty-seven-story, skyscraper in Guangzhou, Guangdong, China. Construction of the tower was completed in 2012. The tower is the eighth-tallest in Guangzhou and the 168th-tallest in the world. == See also == * List of tallest buildings in the world * List of tallest buildings in China * List of tallest buildings in Asia ==References== Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Guangzhou Category:Office buildings completed in 2012
title: Bank of Guangzhou Tower
